Package: background
Version: 0.1-2
Title: Background processing and asynchronous callbacks
Author: Simon Urbanek <simon.urbanek@r-project.org>
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <simon.urbanek@r-project.org>
Description: This package provides infrastructure for servicing
	     asynchronous tasks in R while R is idle. It provides
	     building block from streaming and other asynchnonous
	     processing in R.
License: GPL-2
Suggests: parallel
URL: http://www.rforge.net/background
